CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: VOC Energy Trust is a statutory trust. It is created to acquire and hold a term net profits interest for the benefit of the Trust unitholders. The underlying properties include VOC Brazos' net interests which are located in the states of Kansas and Texas. The trust is entitled to receive most of the net proceeds from the sale of production of oil and natural gas attributable to the underlying properties.
